records.name: Huvafen Fushi Maldives

descriptions.direction: Located in Huvafen Fushi, Huvafen Fushi Maldives is on a private beach. Maldives Islamic Centre and Mulee Aage Palace are local landmarks, and travelers looking to shop may want to visit Orofini Jewellery and Boutique by Island Breeze. Looking to get your feet wet? Windsurfing and fishing adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Upon arrival at Velana International Airport, you'll be greeted by our representative and escorted to our lounge for refreshments before transferring to your speedboat. Enjoy a scenic 40-minute ride across the pristine waters to Huvafen Fushi, our luxury Maldives resort. For seamless transfer, please email your arrival and departure flight details at least 48 hours prior to arrival. Huvafen Fushi, meaning 'Dream Island, ' offers an unparalleled experience. Relax in your private villa with cascading decks and direct access to the ocean for a swim. Indulge in our underwater spa or float at the infinity pool's edge with breathtaking views of the Indian Ocean. The resort, located at the western end of North Malé Atoll, combines convenient proximity to the airport with the tranquility of a secluded island paradise. Check-in is at 2 pm and check-out is at 12 noon.
